info.name: Multiple themes in one
info.description:
I took a few different themes that i have been using for a while and combined them into one.
Themes used:
Extended playlist menu
Extended Favorites menu
lights out
New design fix
Bigger player sizes
Enhancer fix halfcut screen
info.additionalInfo: If anyone knows how to get the channel names to show up on youtube when your using chrome, feel free to post it in like the comments or something. It works fine for firefox, and chrome aswell other then that one thing.
